Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.89,0:06:07.68,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}{\c&B2B2B2}{\bord2.5}案外終わりは近いのかもね
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.02,0:06:18.15,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&516370\4c&516370}{\bord2.5}{\c&DFECF5}能看到城鎮了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:18.15,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&516370\4c&516370}{\bord2.5}{\c&DFECF5}町が見えてきましたね
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.86,0:06:21.78,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&516370\4c&516370}{\bord2.5}{\c&DFECF5}馬車都排著隊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.86,0:06:21.78,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&516370\4c&516370}{\bord2.5}{\c&DFECF5}馬車が並んでいますね
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.78,0:06:23.95,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&516370\4c&516370}{\bord2.5}{\c&DFECF5}那是商人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.78,0:06:23.95,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&516370\4c&516370}{\bord2.5}{\c&DFECF5}ありゃ商人だな
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.95,0:06:26.28,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&516370\4c&516370}{\bord2.5}{\c&DFECF5}因為今晚是解放祭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.95,0:06:26.28,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&516370\4c&516370}{\bord2.5}{\c&DFECF5}今夜は解放祭ですから
