Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:35.00,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&3B3B34\4c&3B3B34}{\bord2.5}{\c&C1CED2}この地域を支配していた魔族を討伐してくださった日です
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.29,0:06:38.29,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2}{\c&DFF3F7}好像是有這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:38.29,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2}{\c&DFF3F7}そんなこともあったっけね
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.84,0:06:43.05,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&6E6870\4c&6E6870}{\bord2}{\c&D8E7EB}解放祭正是那天的紀念日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.84,0:06:43.05,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&6E6870\4c&6E6870}{\bord2}{\c&D8E7EB}解放祭はその日を記念したもので
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.76,0:06:48.30,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&6E5773\4c&6E5773}{\bord2}{\c&EAD3ED}大家會裝飾城鎮中央廣場的銅像
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.76,0:06:48.30,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&6E5773\4c&6E5773}{\bord2}{\c&EAD3ED}町の中央広場にあるヒンメル様たちの像を飾り付け
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.30,0:06:51.47,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&6E5773\4c&6E5773}{\bord2}{\c&EAD3ED}全鎮民眾會一起慶祝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:51.47,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&6E5773\4c&6E5773}{\bord2}{\c&EAD3ED}町全体で盛大に祝うのです
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.22,0:06:54.44,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&DFF3F7}人類真是小題大做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:54.44,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&DFF3F7}人間は大げさだね
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.44,0:06:57.06,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&DFF3F7}動不動就辦慶典
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.44,0:06:57.06,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&DFF3F7}何でもかんでも祭りにしたがる
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.06,0:06:59.27,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&DFF3F7}距離魔族被打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:59.27,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&DFF3F7}魔族が倒されたのは
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.27,0:07:02.19,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&DFF3F7}已經過了80多年了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.27,0:07:02.19,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&DFF3F7}もう80年以上も前になります
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.15,0:07:04.86,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&DFF3F7}{\bord2.5}對人類而言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:04.86,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&DFF3F7}{\bord2.5}人間にとって
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.86,0:07:08.49,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&DFF3F7}{\bord2.5}這是足以忘卻往事的漫長時光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:08.49,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&DFF3F7}{\bord2.5}何かを忘れ去るのに十分過ぎる時間です
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.28,0:07:11.95,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&DFF3F7}即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:11.95,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&DFF3F7}それでも
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.95,0:07:14.04,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&DFF3F7}{\bord2.5}大家在這天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:14.04,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&DFF3F7}{\bord2.5}この日だけは皆
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.04,0:07:16.21,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&DFF3F7}{\bord2.5}仍會想起欣梅爾大人一行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.04,0:07:16.21,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&DFF3F7}{\bord2.5}ヒンメル様たちを思い出すのです
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.21,0:07:16.87,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&DFF3F7}仍會想起欣梅爾大人一行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.21,0:07:16.87,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&DFF3F7}ヒンメル様たちを思い出すのです
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.63,0:07:22.71,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&666666\4c&666666}{\c&D1E0E6}{\bord2.5}做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:22.71,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&666666\4c&666666}{\c&D1E0E6}{\bord2.5}上出来だね
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.55,0:07:26.47,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}{\c&CCCCCC}重做了五次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.55,0:07:26.47,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}{\c&CCCCCC}リテイク５回か
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.47,0:07:29.05,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}{\c&CCCCCC}這次很快就做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.47,0:07:29.05,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}{\c&CCCCCC}今回は早く終わりましたね
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.47,0:07:33.06,Dial-CHI,,0,1444,0,,{\c&D9D9D9}{\bord2.5}你似乎經常請人製作銅像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:33.06,Dial-JPN,,0,1444,0,,{\c&D9D9D9}{\bord2.5}ヒンメルってよく像作ってもらっているよね
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.68,0:07:36.35,Dial-CHI,,1311,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&D9D9D9}我希望被大家記在心裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:36.35,Dial-JPN,,1311,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&D9D9D9}みんなに覚えていてほしいと思ってね
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.44,0:07:39.36,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&D9D9D9}我們和妳不同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.44,0:07:39.36,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&D9D9D9}僕たちは君と違って
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.36,0:07:41.19,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&D9D9D9}不能長生於世
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.36,0:07:41.19,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&D9D9D9}長く生きるわけじゃないから
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.40,0:07:44.11,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&F2F2F2}我這份英姿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.40,0:07:44.11,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&F2F2F2}後世にしっかりと
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.11,0:07:46.70,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&F2F2F2}{\t(1814,2314,\c&CCCCCC\3c&333333\4c&333333\bord3)}必須完整地流傳後世
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:46.70,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&F2F2F2}{\t(1814,2314,\c&CCCCCC\3c&333333\4c&333333\bord3)}僕のイケメンぶりを残しておかないと
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.70,0:07:48.41,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&CCCCCC\3c&333333\4c&333333\bord3}差不多該回旅店了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.70,0:07:48.41,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&CCCCCC\3c&333333\4c&333333\bord3}そろそろ宿に戻ろっか
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.74,0:07:50.57,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&E6E6E6}不過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:50.57,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&E6E6E6}でも
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.49,0:07:52.91,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&E6E6E6}最重要的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:52.91,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&E6E6E6}一番の理由は
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.87,0:07:58.17,Dial-CHI,,1544,0,0,,{\3c&748A8C\4c&748A8C}{\bord2}{\c&DFEEF0}是不希望妳在未來孤身一人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:58.17,Dial-JPN,,1544,0,0,,{\3c&748A8C\4c&748A8C}{\bord2}{\c&DFEEF0}君が未来で一人ぼっちにならないようにするためかな
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.33,0:08:01.29,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}{\c&CCCCCC}什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:01.29,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}{\c&CCCCCC}何それ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.59,0:08:04.17,Dial-CHI,,1411,0,0,,{\3c&748A8C\4c&748A8C}{\bord2}{\c&DFEEF0}我們不是童話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.59,0:08:04.17,Dial-JPN,,1411,0,0,,{\3c&748A8C\4c&748A8C}{\bord2}{\c&DFEEF0}おとぎ話じゃない
