Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:08.43,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\c&E6E6E6}僕たちは確かに実在したんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.43,0:08:15.98,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&3D2B2F\4c&3D2B2F}{\bord2}{\c&BFD7E3}大家每年都會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:15.98,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&3D2B2F\4c&3D2B2F}{\bord2}{\c&BFD7E3}こうやって毎年のように
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.98,0:08:19.81,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&3D2B2F\4c&3D2B2F}{\bord2}{\c&BFD7E3}歌頌勇者欣梅爾一行的豐功偉績
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.98,0:08:19.81,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&3D2B2F\4c&3D2B2F}{\bord2}{\c&BFD7E3}勇者ヒンメル様ご一行の功績をたたえるのです
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.19,0:08:22.77,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&C3D3E0}{\3c&3D2B2F\4c&3D2B2F}{\bord3}說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:22.77,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&C3D3E0}{\3c&3D2B2F\4c&3D2B2F}{\bord3}そういえば
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.77,0:08:24.73,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&C3D3E0}{\3c&3D2B2F\4c&3D2B2F}{\bord3}妳和勇者大人一行的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:24.73,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&C3D3E0}{\3c&3D2B2F\4c&3D2B2F}{\bord3}あなたは勇者様ご一行の
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.73,0:08:27.82,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&3D2B2F\4c&3D2B2F}{\c&C3D3E0}芙莉蓮大人的銅像很像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.73,0:08:27.82,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&3D2B2F\4c&3D2B2F}{\c&C3D3E0}フリーレン様の像によく似ていらっしゃる
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.95,0:08:33.20,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&3D2B2F\4c&3D2B2F}{\bord3}{\c&BFD7E3}一百年後還會繼續辦嗎
