Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.78,0:08:36.20,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&C3D3E0}{\3c&544246\4c&544246}{\bord2.5}只要這個城鎮還在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:36.20,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&C3D3E0}{\3c&544246\4c&544246}{\bord2.5}この町が続く限りは
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.79,0:08:37.96,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&C3D3E0}{\3c&544246\4c&544246}{\bord2.5}那千年之後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.79,0:08:37.96,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&C3D3E0}{\3c&544246\4c&544246}{\bord2.5}千年後は?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.17,0:08:42.21,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&C3D3E0}{\3c&544246\4c&544246}{\bord2.5}那我就不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.17,0:08:42.21,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&C3D3E0}{\3c&544246\4c&544246}{\bord2.5}それは分かりませんな
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.80,0:08:50.38,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&F2F2F2}{\bord2.5}好，走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.80,0:08:50.38,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&F2F2F2}{\bord2.5}よし、行こうか
