Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:53.47,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&F2F2F2}目指すは北の果てだ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.47,0:08:55.81,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&F2F2F2}這麼說來
